    "We use 30,000 financial documents derived from multiple sources covering January 1, 2022 to September 30, 2023.",
    "We use the chain of retrieval, as shown in Figures D.3 and its example is provided in Figure D.4.",
    "We conducted multiple experiments to illustrate the efficacy of the methods described in section 4.",
    "We evaluated our model on the downstream tasks described in section 3.5.",
    "Symbols in the following tables indicate the types of models: ♣, ♠, ♢, ♡, ⋆ and, ■ represent the pre-trained model, the finetuned model, the instruction fine-tuned model, the RL-Tuned Models, tools, and retrieval, respectively."
